# Pinned exactly (not >=) - these are the newest releases that still ship a
# cp310 wheel; the Docker image is python:3.10-slim, and pip-compile's
# resolver otherwise picks the newest overall release first (cp311+/cp313-only
# for these 4) and backtracks through hundreds of older candidate versions
# one at a time trying to find a cp310-compatible one, which is impractically
# slow.
